snippet: Sky View Parc, a mixed-use project in Flushing, Queens, is barreling ahead with its next phase to a very strong reception.
abstract: Sky View Park, mixed-use development in Flushing, Queens is pushing ahead with an expansion after righting itself from recession-era struggles; will add fourth tower containing 235 units in short term, with two more high-rises following over next few years; new development has been met with enthusiasm, with buyers snatching up more than half the units in first day of offering.
lead_paragraph: Sky View Parc, a mixed-use project in Flushing, Queens, is barreling ahead with its next phase to a very strong reception.

headline.seo: More Condos in Flushing, Queens, at Sky View Parc
headline.main: A Robust Reception After a Rocky Start
headline.print_headline: A Robust Reception After a Rocky Start
